msgid "# Deploy vLLM-Ascend with MindIE-Motor"
msgstr "# 使用 MindIE-Motor 部署 vLLM-Ascend"

msgid "## 1. Overview"
msgstr "## 1. 概述"

msgid ""
"[MindIE-Motor](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-PyMotor) provides one-click"
" deployment for **prefill–decode (PD) disaggregation** and **PD "
"aggregation** on Ascend NPUs with vLLM-Ascend. It uses **high-performance "
"scheduling and load balancing**, together with **RAS (Reliability, "
"Availability and Serviceability) capabilities**, to build inference services"
" that are fast and highly stable."
msgstr ""
"[MindIE-Motor](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-PyMotor) 为 vLLM-Ascend 在昇腾 "
"NPU 上提供 **预填充-解码（PD）分离** 和 **PD 聚合** 的一键部署。它利用 **高性能调度与负载均衡**，结合 "
"**RAS（可靠性、可用性与可服务性）能力**，构建快速且高度稳定的推理服务。"

msgid "## 2. Getting Started"
msgstr "## 2. 快速开始"

msgid ""
"For quick deployment instructions, refer to the [MindIE-Motor Quick "
"Start](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-"
"PyMotor/blob/master/docs/zh/user_guide/README.md)."
msgstr ""
"有关快速部署说明，请参考 [MindIE-Motor 快速开始](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-"
"PyMotor/blob/master/docs/zh/user_guide/README.md)。"
